  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "This is a short overview of the code and the developed models for my bachelor thesis with the title \"**Phase Field Methods for Biomedical Growth Processes**\". The thesis was written at the *Institute of Mechanics and Computational Mechanics (IBNM)* at the Leibniz University Hannover, Germany. The examinors were *Prof. Dr.-Ing. Dominik Schillinger* and *Prof. Dr.-Ing. Udo Nackenhorst*. The supervisor was *M. Sc. Etienne Jessen*. The thesis was submitted at September 2020.",
